  "remarks": "A leader of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). As of Jun. 2015, al-Shawakh was the ISIL governor of Aleppo. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed on: 29 Feb. 2016 (amended 6 December 2019)",
